    "description": {
      "value": "This wand has 7 charges for the following properties. It regains 1d6 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the wand crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.\n\nCommand\nWhile holding the wand, you can use an action to expend 1 charge and command another creature to flee or grovel, as with the command spell (save DC 15).\n\nCone of Fear\nWhile holding the wand, you can use an action to expend 3 charges, to cast Fear in a 60-foot cone"
